dil tere dil se jod liya

tujhe vird bana ke yaad kiya

Or jurm kiya hai toh bhi bata, ye jurm ki jurm ki kya hai sazaa

Tumhe hum se badh kar duniya, duniya tumhe humse badhkar
Dil galti kar baitha hai,galti kar baitha hai dil
Haaye dil galti kar baitha tu bol kaffara kya hoga

snippet.title: Two Much With Kajol And Twinkle - Official Trailer | Prime Video India
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
Two Much With Kajol And Twinkle Official Trailer
Starring Kajol, Twinkle Khanna, Salman Khan, Aamir Khan, Govinda, Chunky Panday, Vicky Kaushal, Kriti Sanon, Varun Dhawan, Alia Bhatt, Janhvi Kapoor, Karan Johar.
Created by Banijay Asia

Official Release Date September 25, 2025 on Prime Video India.

About:
Kajol and Twinkle are serving up a talk show with a twist - equal parts masti, magic and maybe even some manic energy. Expect wild hot takes, controversial opinions and the kind of honesty that makes you say, ‚ÄúDude, same!‚Äù 
Joining them are their friends who just happen to be some of the biggest stars in the country (and even the world). With eight unique pairs gracing the couch this season, the conversations jump from filmy nostalgia to family drama, love, paparazzi, fame and everything in between.
What sets it apart is the unapologetic female gaze - a perspective that‚Äôs funny, sharp, and not afraid to hold up a mirror to society. One moment you‚Äôre laughing embarrassingly loudly, the next you‚Äôre caught off guard by an insight that might make you question your own life choices. 
Basically, it‚Äôs a vibe: two women side-by-side, yapping with their friends. Think of it as the fun table at the party, sunny, chatty, and just unhinged enough to keep you hooked.

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PrimeVideoIN/
X: https://x.com/PrimeVideoIN

Additionally, Prime Video‚Äôs video entertainment marketplace, offers customers programming from partners such as Lionsgate Play, Discovery+ Crunchyroll, BBC Player, Sony Pictures ‚Äì Stream, MGM+, FanCode, Chaupal, Manorama Max, Eros Now, Hoichoi, Anime Times, to name a few, via Prime Video add-on-subscriptions, as well as the option to rent movies, regardless of whether customers have a Prime membership or not. Synopsis:
Yash Raj Films‚Äô Saiyaara is an intense love story, that launches Ahaan Panday and Aneet Padda as the next YRF hero and heroine respectively. 

Directed by Mohit Suri, a master of the romance genre, Saiyaara tells a pure-hearted love story of two youngsters Vaani and Krish. While Vaani writes, Krish sings and they both make music together. Though poles apart in their lives, beliefs and backgrounds, Vaani and Krish are perfect with each other and for each other. Will they understand that truth despite their age, their problems? 

They say flawed, imperfect people make for a perfect love story‚Ä¶and Saiyaara is about celebrating that one love story that is so deep, so pure and so caring that it is absolutely unconditional.

Vaani and Krish will have to navigate life, their problems, their insecurities to hopefully realise that only love can be the answer to everything. Saiyaara is a film that celebrates every season of love through the eyes of Vaani & Krish and poses a simple question‚Ä¶do you love someone so much that you would bet everything to keep that person in your life?

Yash Raj Films‚Äô Saiyaara is an intense love story, that launches Ahaan Panday and Aneet Padda as the next YRF hero and heroine respectively. 

Directed by Mohit Suri, a master of the romance genre, Saiyaara tells a pure-hearted love story of two youngsters Vaani and Krish. While Vaani writes, Krish sings and they both make music together. Though poles apart in their lives, beliefs and backgrounds, Vaani and Krish are perfect with each other and for each other. Will they understand that truth despite their age, their problems? 

They say flawed, imperfect people make for a perfect love story‚Ä¶and Saiyaara is about celebrating that one love story that is so deep, so pure and so caring that it is absolutely unconditional.

Vaani and Krish will have to navigate life, their problems, their insecurities to hopefully realise that only love can be the answer to everything. Saiyaara is a film that celebrates every season of love through the eyes of Vaani & Krish and poses a simple question‚Ä¶do you love someone so much that you would bet everything to keep that person in your life?

‚Äî This video is a fan-made concept trailer, created solely for artistic and entertainment purposes.The goal behind this trailer is to showcase my creativity and storytelling skills through a concept trailer based on a unique and original idea. By combining various effects, sound design, and AI technologies, I‚Äôve crafted a cinematic experience that reimagines familiar worlds in bold and imaginative ways. This trailer is not official and is intended to entertain, inspire, and engage with the YouTube community. Thank you for your support ‚Äî now let‚Äôs dive into a world shaped by creativity and craft. üé¨‚ú®

‚Äî In this concept trailer for Wednesday Season 3, the story continues in the aftermath of Season 2 as Wednesday finds herself entangled in an even darker web of family curses and rising threats. Hidden beneath Grandmama Hester‚Äôs watch, Aunt Ophelia resurfaces with a chilling prophecy that Wednesday must die, while Professor Capri and Tyler rally a growing army of Hydes to wage war against Nevermore. At the same time, Enid has vanished into the wilderness, lost to her werewolf form, forcing Wednesday on a relentless search that blurs the line between friend and foe. As ancestral secrets unravel and enemies close in, Wednesday must confront not only the cult determined to claim her bloodline but also the possibility that destiny itself has marked her for destruction. With higher stakes, fractured alliances, and a promise of unrelenting darkness, this new chapter teases a battle where survival may demand the ultimate sacrifice.

It is the Taisho Period in Japan. Tanjiro, a kindhearted boy who sells charcoal for a living, finds his family slaughtered by a demon. To make matters worse, his younger sister Nezuko, the sole survivor, has been transformed into a demon herself.

Though devastated by this grim reality, Tanjiro resolves to become a ‚Äúdemon slayer‚Äù so that he can turn his sister back into a human, and kill the demon that massacred his family.

snippet.title: ‡∞∏‡±ã‡∞Æ‡∞µ‡∞æ‡∞∞‡∞Ç ‡∞∏‡±ç‡∞™‡±Ü‡∞∑‡∞≤‡±ç ‡∞≠‡∞ï‡±ç‡∞§‡∞ø ‡∞™‡∞æ‡∞ü‡∞≤‡±Å | ‡∞≤‡∞ø‡∞Ç‡∞ó‡∞æ‡∞∑‡±ç‡∞ü‡∞ï‡∞Ç | ‡∞¨‡∞ø‡∞≤‡±ç‡∞µ‡∞æ‡∞∑‡±ç‡∞ü‡∞ï‡∞Ç | Monday Lord Shiva Telugu Devotional Songs
snippet.description:
‡∞∏‡±ã‡∞Æ‡∞µ‡∞æ‡∞∞‡∞Ç ‡∞∏‡±ç‡∞™‡±Ü‡∞∑‡∞≤‡±ç ‡∞≠‡∞ï‡±ç‡∞§‡∞ø ‡∞™‡∞æ‡∞ü‡∞≤‡±Å | ‡∞≤‡∞ø‡∞Ç‡∞ó‡∞æ‡∞∑‡±ç‡∞ü‡∞ï‡∞Ç | ‡∞¨‡∞ø‡∞≤‡±ç‡∞µ‡∞æ‡∞∑‡±ç‡∞ü‡∞ï‡∞Ç | Monday Lord Shiva Telugu Devotional Songs


Start your Monday with divine blessings by listening to these special Telugu devotional songs dedicated to Lord Shiva. This collection features the sacred Lingashtakam and Bilvashtakam ‚Äî powerful hymns recited during Monday prayers (Somavaram Bhakti).

Asia Cup 2025 Live

When: Sunday, September 14, 2025 at 6:30 PM local time / 8:00 PM IST

Where: Dubai International Stadium

What to expect: One of the center pitches on the square is being readied for this match. The pitch, as Shivam Dube reckoned after the UAE match, could again be on the slower side, with spinners expected to have more say as the tournament wears on. It's supposed to be a kinder day heat wise, with high temperatures of 39 degrees expected. Dew could still be a factor later in the night, so expect the captain winning the toss to chase.

Team news

India: Ryan ten Doeschate reckoned that India didn't gain "too much information" from their first Asia Cup outing but seemed to suggest that the combinations are likely to stick. That could mean Sanju Samson and Shivam Dube in the middle-order once nire, no Arshdeep Singh, and more game time together for Kuldeep Yadav and Varun Chakaravarthy.

Injuries/unavailability: Shubman Gill was hit in the nets during the optional session on match eve but the Indian vice-captain resumed his batting after a brief timeout and looked alright.

Tactics & matchups: Sanju Samson in the middle order hasn't quite worked before. In T20Is since 2021, Samson has averaged 24 and struck at 139 when batting No.4 or below. His corresponding numbers while batting in the top-three are roughly 37 and 148 respectively. asia cup 2025 live

snippet.title: The Ending That Defines A New Beginning | BGMS FINALS DAY 2 & 3 VLOG | Team GodLike
snippet.description:
Finals Day 2 & 3 wrap up our BGMS Season 4 journey. We had a tough run... the first two days didn‚Äôt go our way at all, and even though we fought back on the last day, it just wasn‚Äôt enough. We finish at #10 overall. Not the result we wanted, not what we worked for.

But that‚Äôs how the game goes. some days you shine, other days you stumble. What matters is we keep learning, keep grinding, and keep moving forward. Thank you to everyone who stood by us through every high and low. Your support means everything to us. On to the next. üíõ

Chinta mite usi ki jo jo tera naam japte, Jai Shree...

Mata bahane sahodar dhyaan tera jo dhare,
Prabhu dhyaan tera jo dhare,
Teri kripa se Baba bhavsagar vo tare, Jai Shree Jeemoot...

Dhoop deep naivedya se jo karte poojan,
Swami jo karte poojan,
Janam janm ke unke kat jaate bandhan, Jai...

Kush durva aur akshat, paan supari chadhe,
Prabhu paan supari chadhe,
Vidhi vidhaan se pooje, Chandra sa bhaagya badhe, Jai Shree...

Jo Shree Jeemoot Vahan ji ki aarti hai karte,
Teri aarti jo karte,
Kaal bhi us dvaare par aane se darte.
